description:
Lazarus tells of seven miraculous signs of Jesus. Lazarus became the last of those signs when Jesus raised him from the dead.

Scripture
John 2:1-11, John 4:46-50, John 5:1-5, John 6:5-14, John 9:1-7, John 11:11-45

Director: Phil Smith
Stars: Ricco Fajardo

chapters.title: Second Miraculous Sign Was a Physical Healing
